<div class="page-header-banner">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="span12">
                <h1><%= pageName %></h1>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <% if (typeof(errors) != 'undefined') { %>
    <script type="text/javascript">
    var errors = <%- errors %>;
    var values = <%- values %>;
    </script>
    <% } %>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="span7">
            <h2>A few details...</h2>
            <form class="form-horizontal" method="post" id="create-board">
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>Administrator</legend>
                    <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="owner">Email address</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <input type="email" name="owner" placeholder="Email goes here..." />
                        
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>Board properties</legend>
                    <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="board-name">Board name</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <input type="text" name="board-name" placeholder="Board name (optional)" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>Access</legend>
                    <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="password-admin">Password</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <input type="password" onmouseover="this.title=this.value" name="password-admin" placeholder="" />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% if ((typeof(captcha) != undefined) && (captcha.type != 'none')) { %>
                        <% if (captcha.type == 'captcha') { %>
	                    	<img src="/img/captcha.jpg" class="captcha" />
	                    	<div class="control-group">
		                        <label class="control-label" for="pdigits">Captcha</label>
		                        <div class="controls">
		                            <input type="text" name="digits"/>
		                        </div>
		                    </div>
                    	<% } else { %>
                    	    <div class="control-group">
	                    	<script type="text/javascript">
						    var RecaptchaOptions = {
						       theme : 'clean',
						       lang  : 'en'
						    };
							</script>
							<%- captcha.form %>
							</div>
                    	<% } %>
                    <% } %>
                </fieldset> 
         
                <div class="control-group" >  
                    <div class="form-actions">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Create board</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn leave">Cancel</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <fieldset>
                    <legend>Grids</legend>
                    <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="grid-size">Card size increments</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <select name="grid-size">
                                <option value="none">Any</option>
                                <option value="small">Small</option>
                                <option value="medium">Medium</option>
                                <option value="large">Large</option>
                            </select>
                            
                        </div>
                        <div class="control-group">
                        <label class="control-label" for="grid-position">Position grid size</label>
                        <div class="controls">
                            <select name="grid-position">
                                <option value="none">Any</option>
                                <option value="small">Small</option>
                                <option value="medium">Medium</option>
                                <option value="large">Large</option>
                            </select>
                            
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    </div>
                </fieldset>                    
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="span5">
            <h2>Help</h2>
            <p class="lead">The best bit about this that almost all of these fields are optional!</p>
            <h3>Email <span class="text-error">- required</span> </h3>
            <p>Your email is used to remind you of your board 
            password<% if (typeof(board) !== 'undefined' && typeof(board.expiry) !== 'undefined') { %>
            , and to inform you when your board is about to expire (currently after <%=board.expiry %> days of inactivity)</p>
            <% } %>. No selling this or spamming you.
            <h3>Board name <span class="text-success">- optional</span></h3>
            <p>Completely optional, but hey it makes it all a bit more personal!</p>
            <h3>Password <span class="text-success">- optional</span></h3>
            <p>If you want to prevent access to your board enter a password here.</p>
            <p>Hover over the password box to see what you've entered already.</p>        
            <p class="text-warning">Warning: not setting a password leaves your board open to abuse by those wishing to do bad.</p>
            <p class="text-muted">We're adding more fine-grained access controls soon e.g. read-only, edit but no admin, etc.</p>
            <h3>Captcha <span class="text-error">- required</span></h3>
            <p>Your not a 'bot are you? Are you? Check things can change very quickly these days.
       </div>
    </div>

</div> <!-- /container -->